data.description: BEAUTIFUL Romanelli & Hughes custom designed, ranch style home, located in POPULAR Linworth Village! SOARING ceilings showcased in the foyer entry to MASSIVE Great RM. featuring corner fireplace & access to 3 Season RM. DELUXE Owner's bedroom with on-suite bath & w/walk-in closet. 1st floor laundry. ENJOY additional living space found in the finished lower level w/full bath & ample unfinished storage space.  THIS HOME IS A MUST SEE! Please note: needs cosmetic work and priced accordingly.
